<br>
Get run3, then level.  AAs some at the same rate, whether you are level 51 or level 60.  So, with epic you might get an AA an hour in FG at level 51.. but you will definately get an AA an hour at level 60 in FG.  And at 60, you will be more effective.  <br>
<br>
Definately, levels.<br>
<br>
Level 61 Arch Mage with 24AAs - master of soloing FG, which I still do frequently.<br>
<br>
BTW - hint for FG soloing to make it really rock.. get your Disease resist to 150.  It sounds way hard, but trust me, its worth every pp!  Once you get near 150, suddenly your pet (and you) will resist 95% of the spells those shrooms toss your way.  Espically the slow.  That makes a HUGE difference.  If your gonna solo FG, get resist up.  Period. (mine is 160+ ATM)  <br>
